{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3b1af18218","title":"会见马里国家元首特拉奥雷时的谈话（节录）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5ebf73d859","index":0,"year":1973,"month":6,"day":22,"articleId":"3b1af18218"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji51","name":"毛泽东全集第51卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/51-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji51":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e22203f556","type":"title","text":"会见马里国家元首特拉奥雷时的谈话（节录）","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"3b1af18218"},{"id":"90680ba05d","type":"paragraph","text":"我们都是叫作第三世界，就是叫作发展中的国家。你不要看我国有什么展览会啊，其实啊，是一个很穷的国家。我说，Isay（英文：我说），越穷越好！就会革命啊。西方国家呢，不大行了。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"3b1af18218"},{"id":"53416508fa","type":"paragraph","text":"无论怎么样，这些西方资本主义国家是创造了文化，创造了科学，创造了工业。现在我们第三世界可以利用他们的科学、工业、文化——包括语言一—的好的部分。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"3b1af18218"},{"id":"5dd26bd0db","type":"paragraph","text":"1973年6月22日，毛泽东会见马里共和国总理特拉奥雷。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"3b1af18218"}],"page":{"id":"247bf9731a","publicationId":"maoquanji51","articleId":"3b1af18218","start":413,"end":413}}}},"__N_SSG":true}